\begin{align*}
\sin n \omega t \ast \cos n \omega t &amp;= \lim_{T \rightarrow \infty} \frac{2}{T} \int_{-\frac{T}{2}}^{\frac{T}{2}} \sin(n\omega \tau) \cos[n\omega (t-\tau)] \mathrm{d}\tau \\
&amp;= \lim_{T \rightarrow \infty} \frac{2}{T} \int_{-\frac{T}{2}}^{\frac{T}{2}} \frac { \sin(n\omega t) + \sin[n\omega (2\tau - t)] } {2} \mathrm{d}\tau \\
&amp;= \lim_{T \rightarrow \infty} \frac{\sin(n\omega t)}{T} \int_{-\frac{T}{2}}^{\frac{T}{2}} \mathrm{d}\tau + \lim_{T \rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{T} \int_{-\frac{T}{2}}^{\frac{T}{2}} \sin[n\omega (2\tau - t)] \mathrm{d}\tau \\
&amp;= \lim_{T \rightarrow \infty} \frac{\sin(n\omega t)}{T} \int_{-\frac{T}{2}}^{\frac{T}{2}} \mathrm{d}\tau \\
&amp;= \lim_{T \rightarrow \infty} \sin(n\omega t) \\
&amp;= \sin(n\omega t)
\end{align*}

div.data-content:
$$
\begin{align*}
\sin n \omega t \ast \cos n \omega t &= \lim_{T \rightarrow \infty} \frac{2}{T} \int_{-\frac{T}{2}}^{\frac{T}{2}} \sin(n\omega \tau) \cos[n\omega (t-\tau)] \mathrm{d}\tau \\
&= \lim_{T \rightarrow \infty} \frac{2}{T} \int_{-\frac{T}{2}}^{\frac{T}{2}} \frac { \sin(n\omega t) + \sin[n\omega (2\tau - t)] } {2} \mathrm{d}\tau \\
&= \lim_{T \rightarrow \infty} \frac{\sin(n\omega t)}{T} \int_{-\frac{T}{2}}^{\frac{T}{2}} \mathrm{d}\tau + \lim_{T \rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{T} \int_{-\frac{T}{2}}^{\frac{T}{2}} \sin[n\omega (2\tau - t)] \mathrm{d}\tau \\
&= \lim_{T \rightarrow \infty} \frac{\sin(n\omega t)}{T} \int_{-\frac{T}{2}}^{\frac{T}{2}} \mathrm{d}\tau \\
&= \lim_{T \rightarrow \infty} \sin(n\omega t) \\
&= \sin(n\omega t)
\end{align*}
$$

\end{align*}
$$
